* 速成/簡易
* [http://hyperrate.com/thread.php?tid=16772 標點簡易] {{Wayback|url=http://hyperrate.com/thread.php?tid=16772 |date=20201024115032 }}
* 大易
* 行列
* [http://hyperrate.com/thread.php?tid=23584 行列大字集] {{Wayback|url=http://hyperrate.com/thread.php?tid=23584 |date=20201203171621 }}
